  ## CONSUMES ## Event
  gEfiIfrRefreshIdOpGuid
  ## CONSUMES ## HII
  ## PRODUCES ## Variable:L"MyIfrNVData"
  ## SOMETIMES_CONSUMES ## Variable:L"MyIfrNVData"
