  ## SOMETIMES_PRODUCES ## GUID  # HiiGetBrowserData MyEfiVar
  ## SOMETIMES_CONSUMES ## GUID  # HiiSetBrowserData MyEfiVar
  gDriverSampleFormSetGuid

[Protocols]
